answers.body_markdown:
Found it. You need to add these inside `generate` tag in pom.xml:

```
&lt;pojos&gt;true&lt;/pojos&gt;
&lt;pojosAsJavaRecordClasses&gt;true&lt;/pojosAsJavaRecordClasses&gt;
```

